Package: caret-data
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: common data files for Caret
 This package provides online help, tutorials and atlas datasets for Caret.
 It enables the following functionality in Caret:
 .
  - Map volumes to surface via PALS atlas
  - Multi-resolution morphing
  - Projection of foci via PALS atlas
  - Surface-based registration
  - Surface flattening
